      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "You don’t close that gap with a better architecture. You close it with line-side feedback, a labelling queue, and a retraining cadence the quality team actually trusts. Models hit a number on a benchmark. Systems hold a number under load."
